{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_baslin_set_1", "eventName": "晚霞下的演奏", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "晚霞下的演奏", "storyInfo": "作為魯珀坎的貴族繼承人之一，米夏埃爾奉命前往首都“接受教育”。在令他畏懼的雙子女皇面前，無足輕重的他盡力為故鄉爭取機會。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g8_towersquare", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "12月28日 5:00 P.M."}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "崔林特爾梅，雙子女皇塔前"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "m", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米夏埃爾抱著對他來說過於沉重的低音號，帶著樂隊，跟隨接待他的侍從走向雙子塔。"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米夏埃爾閣下，您出發的時候，家鄉應該已經在籌備新年活動了吧？", "name": "負責接待的侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叫我米夏埃爾就好。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，好。", "name": "負責接待的侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真懷念啊，家鄉的晚霞或許沒有崔林特爾梅的燦爛，但烤扭結餅的香味，是什麼東西都沒辦法替代的……", "name": "負責接待的侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到您會在這個時間到達崔林特爾梅，我以為……", "name": "負責接待的侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您至少會在自己的高塔裡度過新年。", "name": "負責接待的侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟這可能是我在家鄉過的最後一個新年了，對吧？被送到崔林特爾梅“學習”的繼承人們，不知道什麼時候才能回到家鄉。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是我堅持想要趕上首都的新年慶典的。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您想參加新年慶典？……", "name": "負責接待的侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天覲見時，我就會向兩位女皇提出申請。父親說了，要想其他大區在貿易上平等地對待魯珀坎，首先，得看陛下們的態度。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，陛下們……啊，米夏埃爾，再往前我就不被允許過去了。雖然我沒進去過，但前往恩典高塔的路應該就是那條。", "name": "負責接待的侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你從來沒進去過？……那過去幾年裡，從家鄉遞給陛下們的官方文書，都是誰在傳遞？", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#10$2"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……陛下們不想聽的時候，鮮有“雜音”能傳到她們的耳朵裡。這些“特殊禮遇”，周圍的貴族也全一清二楚。", "name": "負責接待的侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，米夏埃爾，和陛下們說話千萬小心啊。我聽說過很多不好的傳聞。", "name": "負責接待的侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尤其是那位赫琳瑪特——差點把我們的家鄉踏平的那位——聽說要是有人說錯半個字，她就會用腰間那把劍把那人砍成兩半！", "name": "負責接待的侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您可不要以為這些都是危言聳聽！盡量多和那位和善親切的伊維格娜德交流，畢竟您的安全才是最重要的……", "name": "負責接待的侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#2$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為這場覲見準備了一整年，算不算足夠小心？", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#2$2"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#2$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從自我介紹，到選曲介紹詞，到參加新年慶典申請書的每個詞，光是寫稿子都寫爛了好幾支筆呢。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#2$2"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#8$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，終於有魯珀坎的狼被允許踏入羊群的高塔，這本來就是個好訊號，不是嗎？", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#8$2"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……祝您一切順利，米夏埃爾。", "name": "負責接待的侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米夏埃爾走上了那條陌生且過於寬闊的道路。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（呼——吸——呼——吸——）", "name": "米夏埃爾"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g6_towerterrace", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（只有……一位女皇在場？還有一些文武官員。那位令人害怕的赫琳瑪特不在？）", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（太好了……許多特意為她準備的說辭用不上了。）", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他走上前時，能聽到自己轟隆作響的心跳。他向伊維格娜德行禮，動作穩重而收斂，如之前預演過無數次那般。"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "all", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "all", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下，米夏埃爾代表家族前來覲見。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米夏埃爾，到了這裡還適應嗎？", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#10$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#8$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一切都很好，感謝您的關心。這裡到處是我在家鄉未曾見過的景色。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#8$2"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#8$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "目睹了首都的繁榮，我更加期待在“永恆恩典”與“無情權威”的照耀下，魯珀坎也能、跟上發展的腳步。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#8$2"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米夏埃爾的心抽緊了一下。因為緊張，在他流利的對答中出現了一個幾乎無法察覺的小停頓。"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他偷偷觀察伊維格娜德的反應，發現她臉上的笑容依舊親切，彷彿在鼓勵他不要害怕。米夏埃爾心裡緊繃的弦終於放鬆了些許。"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看你帶著樂隊，這次帶來了怎樣的演奏？", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是一首來自我家鄉的敘事曲——《白牙》。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它講述的，是叢林中茹毛飲血的野獸，有一日走到叢林邊緣時，被遠處傳來的樂聲吸引，並為之感動……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是它們收起獠牙，走出叢林，迎接了樂聲的感召。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（她明白我選曲的用意！而且看起來也很滿意……太好了。）", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽聽你對這首曲子的演繹吧。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。請允許我代表魯珀坎將接下來的演奏獻給女皇陛下！", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g6_towerterrace", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來自魯珀坎的敘事曲響徹高塔。高音活潑明快，低音溫潤順從，年輕的狼向女皇收起了獠牙。"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "選曲無疑投了伊維格娜德所好。但是，為了進一步留下好印象，米夏埃爾在最後的低音號獨奏中還留了一手。"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一拍、二拍、三拍、四拍——所有樂器收聲，米夏埃爾上前一步，開始了他經過刻苦練習、精妙絕倫的獨奏。"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這段獨奏與原版聽起來不一樣。原版質樸而深情，但那配不上伊維格娜德對高貴華麗的喜好。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，米夏埃爾為它加入了觸感完美的滑音，給每一個音區賦予更豐富的色彩。"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看這金碧輝煌的恩典高塔、隨處飄舞的彩色錦缎，還有抬頭就能欣賞的、鋪滿天際的晚霞——"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "華麗的音色和絢爛的演奏技巧與高塔主人的喜好正相合，它金光燦爛，它光輝聖潔，它——萬幸，被完美地演繹了出來！"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這完全沒有辜負他過去一年的準備！米夏埃爾的心激動得狂跳。他緩緩放下低音號，滿心期待地偷看伊維格娜德的臉色。"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（太好了，她看起來仍然很親切。）", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#7$2"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（……不過，她的表情是不是和演奏開始前一模一樣？）", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米夏埃爾與樂隊一起向伊維格娜德鞠了個躬。"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。曲子選得蠻好的。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "改編也很用心。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們是花了心思的。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#9$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能得到您的欣賞，我十分榮幸。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#9$2"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下，事實上，我此次前來，也是想為父親傳達幾句話。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "父親希望能就魯珀坎貴族參與新年慶典的事，聽聽您的意見……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必了。難得聽到這麼合心意的演奏，我哪裡還有心情考慮這種事？以後再議吧。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米夏埃爾的手心頓時冒出了冷汗。"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那、可否與您商議一個日後再議的時間？", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#10$2"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "魯珀坎很渴望跟上其他大區的腳步，希望有機會更好地建設我們共同的萊塔尼亞……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#10$2"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你對音樂的熱忱已經透過演奏傳遞給我了。比起新年慶典，有更適合你的安排。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今後，你就去馬蒂的塔裡做事。那裡藏有豐富的古樂譜，既然想要迎接樂聲的感召，沒有比那裡更適合的地方了。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叢林裡的小狼，我的安排，你滿意嗎？", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米夏埃爾感到自己手裡的低音號越來越沉重，對他苦苦支撐的手臂帶來尖銳的疼痛。"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠離女皇的高塔，古樂譜——想被冷落多久，就被冷落多久……"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的一生突然在這樣一個短短的接見中，被輕描淡寫地宣告。而這是一個無法說不的場景。這就是，親切和善的伊維格娜德……"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……願……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……！", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#5$2"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人都往開門聲望去，出現在門口的是萊塔尼亞的另一位女皇，赫琳瑪特——"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位兩年前親自出征米夏埃爾的家鄉，以絕對的武力鎮壓反叛的“無情權威”。米夏埃爾的臉色更蒼白了。"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1115_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "赫琳瑪特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1115_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫琳瑪特……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#5$2"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來了。可惜來遲了，錯過了這位魯珀坎少年特地為我們準備的精彩演奏。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1115_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在外面就聽到了。難聽至極。", "name": "赫琳瑪特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1115_1#8$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀？我還以為這樣伶俐的孩子會討你喜歡呢。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#3$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1115_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "浮誇、華而不實。最後獨奏的改編更是不堪入耳。", "name": "赫琳瑪特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1115_1#11$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真可惜，本來還想送他去馬蒂的塔裡研習呢。", "name": "伊維格娜德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1115_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "研習？這種水準，還是趁早滾回魯珀坎吧。", "name": "赫琳瑪特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1115_1#11$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是，我先、退下了。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#2$2"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莉澤洛特，我看你又在忙新年慶典的事？這種事交給女皇之聲去辦就好，何必浪費你的時間。", "name": "身後傳來的嚴厲聲音"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "魯珀坎的聲音總得有人來聽。", "name": "身後傳來的溫和聲音"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不去聽，聲音就不從各個角落鑽進耳朵裡了嗎？", "name": "身後傳來的溫和聲音"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那還不如開誠布公，見上一面。", "name": "身後傳來的溫和聲音"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"yime": 2.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫琳瑪特是如何回答的，米夏埃爾已經聽不清了。他已經走到了門口，不敢再逗留，只能退了出去。"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（魯珀坎的聲音……？家鄉從正常管道寄來的書信，不是都被拒之門外了嗎？難道是有人……）", "name": "米夏埃爾"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g5_noblehall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#2$2"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1115_1#1$1", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "赫琳瑪特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1115_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……！", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#5$2"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1115_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫琳瑪特，請留步。請原諒我的冒昧，我想對您剛才的搭救表示感謝。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#10$2"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫琳瑪特，請……", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想……！我相信，您會在這個時候出現，並非偶然——", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米夏埃爾情急之下拋出的話語，終於讓赫琳瑪特的腳步為他停留。他望著女皇沉默的背影，艱難地吞嚥了一口唾沫。"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1115_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我看來，在高塔外被冷落數年的侍從，和剛來一天就被訓斥的我，我們的存在，本質上是女皇們態度的延伸。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一位魯珀坎的少年被女皇當眾責難，又被另一位女皇當眾放過，這——不會是一個巧合。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場戲的觀眾是在場的貴族，和那些削尖了腦袋，把信送到女皇面前的，魯珀坎貴族的繼承人們——", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米夏埃爾觀察了赫琳瑪特片刻，那紋絲不動的後背沒有向他透露任何資訊。"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1115_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……而這個演員究竟是否必須是我，我仍沒有結論。也許是二位不喜歡我父親的主張，又也許，只是我到達的時間不巧。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只知道，您救下了我。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我剛才的猜測都成立，那麼您的舉動也是女皇給我們的訊息之一。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我更能確信，女皇對魯珀坎仍懷有仁慈之心。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1115_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看你和莉澤洛特的交流，我以為你會是個更謹慎的孩子。", "name": "赫琳瑪特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1115_1#2$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您喜歡直截了當，我就有話直說。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不喜歡今天的曲子——", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實，我也不喜歡今天的編曲。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我寧願冒著冒犯您的危險，也要在這裡等待您的原因。", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還會許多曲子，我希望有機會，能吹給您聽……！", "name": "米夏埃爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4109_baslin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫琳瑪特沉默地邁開腳步，彷彿剛才從背後傳來的，只是不值一提的雜音。米夏埃爾望著她遠去的背影，心一點一點沉入絕望之中。"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "忽然，女皇的腳步停頓了一下。那一剎那，他似乎看到女皇的臉偏轉過來。他沒有等來任何指示，赫琳瑪特繼續向前走去。"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米夏埃爾從未像那一刻那般不顧一切。他顧不上思考自己有沒有看錯、有沒有會錯意，他毫不猶豫地追上了赫琳瑪特的步伐。"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}